# Task Management API (RBAC)

A small Task Management API built with **Node.js** and **Express** that supports **JWT authentication** and **role-based access control (RBAC)**.

Users can be **Admin, Manager, or User**, and their role determines what tasks they can manage.

---

## Features

- User authentication with JWT
- Role-based permissions: Admin, Manager, User
- CRUD operations on tasks
- In-memory storage (no database)
- Proper error handling (401, 403, 404, 500)

---

## Roles & Permissions

| Role    | Permissions on Tasks                     |
| ------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Admin   | Create, Read all, Update any, Delete any |
| Manager | Create, Read all, Update own only        |
| User    | Create, Read own only, Update own only   |

---

## Endpoints

- **POST /user/login** → Get JWT
- **POST /task/create** → Create task
- **GET /task/gettask** → Get tasks (all or own depending on role)
- **PUT /task/update//:id** → Update task
- **DELETE /task/delete/:id** → Delete task (Admin only)

---

## hwo to start

step 1:-
npm i  
step 2:-
npm run dev
